1. Can you provide specific details on the year and age when Virat Kohli made his first-class debut in cricket after representing the Delhi team at various age-group levels?
2. Is there credible evidence to confirm that Virat Kohli indeed captained the India under-19 cricket team to victory at the 2008 under-19 World Cup in Malaysia?
3. Which year did Virat Kohli make his One Day International (ODI) debut for India, and against which team was the match played?
